Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.67,0:22:50.47,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(620,180)\blur1}無助  彷徨之時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:22:55.97,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(620,180)\blur1}一直盡可能的尋找著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:23:00.02,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(620,180)\blur1}可以拉住我的手的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:05.48,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(620,180)\blur1}不斷受傷  不斷微笑
